data.description: Welcome to a fantastic 4-bedroom home with a thoughtfully designed split floorplan, centrally located off Leroy Coffer Highway between Richmond Hill and Fort Stewart. Enjoy the perks of no city taxes and no HOA. The charm continues with a side-entry garage, elegant formal dining room, and an all-brick exterior.  Step into a generously sized, fenced backyard featuring a covered porch – an ideal retreat for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. The master bathroom offers a luxurious large tub, and the home is bathed in ample natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Cozy up by the fireplace during chilly evenings, and appreciate the stylish touch of white cabinetry in the well-appointed kitchen.
